						<font face="verdana" color="#6B5A39" size="+1">
							<a name="Voting, Please take it seriously, Vote!">Voting, Please take it seriously, Vote!
					</td>
					<td align="right">
						<font face="verdana" color="#6B5A39" size="-2">
						Tuesday, May&nbsp;29
					</td>
				<tr>
					<td colspan="2">
						<font face="verdana" color="#BFBFBF" size="-1">
						<div align="justify">
							Folks--<br><br>

Take advantage of your ability to vote on members and council. Voting shows that you take your membership in the guild seriously, that you care about who gets in , and who helps run things. Not all guilds have votes.. many let everyone in, and the leader makes all the rules.<br><br>

We will lose good prospects if we cannot get them through the selection process quickly. Maybe we need to revamp the process a bit. Or maybe people need to take the time to learn about the prospects, and then vote. With an active membership at 29 ( although some on the active list dont seem to be active) it shouldn't take us so long to vote.<br><br>

So lets all exercise our priveledge as a guild member and vote! Or I will get out the cattle prod and follow folks around until they vote!<br><br>

Seriously folks, take a few minutes, read the apps, and make a choice.
							<br>~ <a href="mailto:eqaddicts@earthlink.net">Gladewalker</a><br><br>
							<center><hr size="1" color="#6B5A39" width="200"><center>
						</div>
					</td>
				</tr>
				</table><br>
				
