					</td>
					<td align="right">
						<font face="verdana" color="#6B5A39" size="-2">
						Tuesday, May&nbsp;22
					</td>
				<tr>
					<td colspan="2">
						<font face="verdana" color="#BFBFBF" size="-1">
						<div align="justify">
							On Wednesday the 23rd I would like to get some guild events going. We have a few options and perhaps can more than one done! Help Lanath out. Help Gladewalker, and go to the Tower of Frozen Shadow to get more keys!<br><br>

Expect festivitys to start as soon as we can get people together. I urge those of you who get online before me to start things up if possible. Tomorrow afternoon I also have a bunch of posts and replies to make so keep checking the forums.
							<br>~ <a href="mailto:Boisvertbladesong@hotmail.com">Boisvert</a><br><br>
							<center><hr size="1" color="#6B5A39" width="200"><center>
						</div>
