							<a name="Coming Events">Coming Events
					</td>
					<td align="right">
						<font face="verdana" color="#6B5A39" size="-2">
						Monday, May&nbsp;21
					</td>
				<tr>
					<td colspan="2">
						<font face="verdana" color="#BFBFBF" size="-1">
						<div align="justify">
							I haven't forgotten just looking for time to fit in our upcoming events! My weekends for the next month are pretty busy so I'm looking for time to get our Charok raid in. Depending on the roster make-up this might be an exploratory raid with the goal to get down to the Royals area and gear up for a marathon so that the following raid we can go down there and get the epic parts we need.<br><br>

We also have a bunch of weekday events I would like to see if we can get going. Gladewalker could use help in the Rathemoutains on Hill Giants for his epic. Lanath needs help in Nekutlos Forest for his epic. Blackeyed and Meadmid both need help in the Temple of Solusek Ro for their epic. All of the above(Sorry for any I might have forgotten) are relativly small raids and should take no more than an evening each to get done. Perhaps we can even get a couple in one night.
							<br>~ <a href="mailto:Boisvertbladesong@hotmail.com">Boisvert</a><br><br>
							<center><hr size="1" color="#6B5A39" width="200"><center>
						</div>
