						<div align="justify">
							All Members should visit the Memebers Only section and post their thoughts about a myriad of issues Mercurial has brought up. This Saturday, after collecting feedback from everyone, I would like to have a meeting somewhere in Norrath. I would like to also get a raid going somewhere the rest of the day, somewhere all members can go. I was possibly thinking TT or LOIO for the Prod for HS keys.
							<br>~ <a href="mailto:Boisvertbladesong@hotmail.com">Boisvert</a><br><br>
