							<a name="Plane of Fear">Plane of Fear
					</td>
					<td align="right">
						<font face="verdana" color="#6B5A39" size="-2">
						Sunday, May&nbsp;6
					</td>
				<tr>
					<td colspan="2">
						<font face="verdana" color="#BFBFBF" size="-1">
						<div align="justify">
							Many thanks to those of you who gave your Friday evening to come to Fear with us. We only lost a handfull on the break in. A few from the feign death team and a few from the last groups to come in who we didn't call soon enough!<br><br>

After that we proceded to walk through the zone, with only whipeout late that night or early morning depending on how you look at it, when we tried Terror for the first time. In the end all three golems died! A special note to Bryionak who let Daimyo loot the Shiverback Jerkin, Javen who let Gladewalker loot the Vermiculated gloves, and Gladewalker for taking a couple DT's for the team!
							<br>~ <a href="mailto:Boisvertbladesong@hotmail.com">Boisvert</a><br><br>
